name: SPRINT (Prototype)
description:
Roguelike with randomly-generated levels where each level has a time limit. 

GOAL

Eliminate enemies before the time runs out.

PLAYER

Can slash, shoot, double jump, climb

CONTROLS
  • A, D                      move
  • S                            pass through
  • Left click           slash
  • Right click        shoot 
  • Space                 jump, double jump 
  • Space + A/D    climb 
  • P                            debug
ISSUE NOTICE
- The file size is weirdly big
